  "description": "A majestic owl perches on a thin, bare branch amidst lush greenery. The owl has striking golden eyes, a mottled brown and white plumage, and distinctive ear tufts. Its feathers display intricate patterns of light and dark stripes. The background is a blurred mix of green foliage and soft, out-of-focus lights, creating a natural, woodland setting. The branch it's resting on is horizontal and extends across the frame. The lighting is soft and diffused, highlighting the owl's features and the texture of its feathers.",
